29:59.423 --> 30:01.288
I want my songs to sound like me.

30:01.384 --> 30:02.544
They do.

30:02.718 --> 30:03.878
Oh, the fuck they do. They do not.

30:04.428 --> 30:06.544
Make me sound like some fuckin'

30:06.681 --> 30:08.763
dime-a-dozen Nashville cupcake.

30:09.225 --> 30:10.431
(EXHALES)

30:10.685 --> 30:13.301
Look, I thought you made a choice here.

30:13.396 --> 30:15.102
I did not choose this.

30:16.774 --> 30:19.561
Don't mind me.
Ijust sit in the booth and push knobs.

30:19.652 --> 30:21.813
I forget everything I hear
by the end of the session.

30:21.904 --> 30:24.020
Let's go get a drink someplace.

30:24.115 --> 30:25.946
I don't need a drink.

30:26.033 --> 30:29.366
I need my sound on my fucking record.

30:33.916 --> 30:35.907
(PLAYING UPBEAT MUSIC)

30:41.757 --> 30:45.591
You can take your time Well, I don't mind

30:45.678 --> 30:47.464
I don't mind

30:50.016 --> 30:53.804
