30:53.894 --> 30:55.885
Well, I don't mind

30:58.691 --> 31:02.183
Just as long as this love is strong

31:02.278 --> 31:04.269
Well, I don't mind...

31:22.381 --> 31:24.087
What?

31:24.175 --> 31:26.882
What? Come on.

31:26.969 --> 31:30.177
You know,
I need a steady gig, something, anything,

31:30.264 --> 31:32.346
just so I can feel it once in a while.

31:32.433 --> 31:34.640
Why do you think I dragged you here tonight?

31:34.810 --> 31:37.062
