31:38.731 --> 31:40.312
I know who I married.

31:48.783 --> 31:50.489
(PLAYING BE YOU)

32:34.912 --> 32:36.618
(CROWD APPLAUDING)

32:38.958 --> 32:42.371
Thank you. Thank you.
That was Be You by Jon Batiste.

32:42.461 --> 32:43.997
(CROWD CHEERING)

32:46.215 --> 32:49.878
Now I'd like to bring
up one of our friends from back home.

32:49.969 --> 32:52.426
Please welcome the great Nicholas Payton.

32:52.513 --> 32:54.378
(CROWD CHEERING)

33:00.062 --> 33:01.017
Yes, indeed.

33:01.105 --> 33:03.687
Look like we got a New Orleans
quorum up in here tonight, huh?

33:03.774 --> 33:05.685
Yeah, I know it,
but I gotta come all the way to New York

33:05.776 --> 33:06.856
to play with my homeboys.

33:06.944 --> 33:08.730
Tell 'em your business, brah.

33:12.199 --> 33:14.190
(PLAYING JAZZ MUSIC)

