36:41.408 --> 36:42.363
Clean it up

36:42.451 --> 36:43.736
All the paper and trash

36:43.827 --> 36:45.692
-Clean it up
-Get that stuff outta here

36:45.954 --> 36:47.615
Clean up after Mardi Gras...

36:47.706 --> 36:48.912
Sorry to hear that, man.

36:48.999 --> 36:50.580
It was a great after-school program,

36:50.667 --> 36:52.077
which is why I called you, Derrick.

36:52.169 --> 36:54.034
His best kids need a place to land.

36:54.129 --> 36:55.289
I could take a few.

36:55.464 --> 36:56.624
Yeah? Roots of Music?

36:56.715 --> 36:58.046
There's a waiting list, but...

36:58.133 --> 37:01.091
Oh, man. Come on, this would be so good.

37:01.178 --> 37:03.419
I was worried I was gonna
have to let them all down, you know?

37:03.514 --> 37:05.129
I got you, man. We goin' take them. I got ya.

37:05.849 --> 37:07.680
Okay. Thanks, man.

37:07.768 --> 37:10.805
