38:46.867 --> 38:51.327
If I give you the songs,
then you give me the package.

38:51.413 --> 38:54.655
I have to have that much,
or I can't do what I do.

38:59.922 --> 39:01.082
Deal.

39:05.469 --> 39:09.303
You know what, Annie?
I do believe you're gonna make it.

39:09.806 --> 39:12.013
